      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/23/2/116/3",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ص قَالَ اللَّهُ جَلَّ جَلَالُهُ یَا ابْنَ آدَمَ اذْکُرْنِی بَعْدَ الْغَدَاهِ سَاعَهً وَ بَعْدَ الْعَصْرِ سَاعَهً أَکْفِکَ مَا أَهَمَّکَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "3.  Imam  Muhammad  Baqir  (a.s.)  narrates  that  the  Holy Prophet  (s.a.w.s.)  said  that  Allah,  the  Might  and  Sublime said,  “O  children  of  Adam!  Remember  Me  after  Morning Prayer for an hour and after Asr prayers for an hour so that I fulfill your important wishes.”"
        ]
      }
    },
